text: Igor Atrokhov (born 18 January 1960) is a Russian equestrian. He competed in the individual eventing at the 2008 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1960 births Category:Living people Category:Russian male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Russia Category:Equestrians at the 2008 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Moscow
